```plantuml
@startuml onlybakam_reinvent2022-vote-app

actor User
participant "Next.js Frontend" as Frontend
participant "AWS AppSync" as AppSync
participant "AWS Lambda: AddVote Resolver" as AddVoteResolver
participant "SNS Publisher" as SNSPublisher
participant "DynamoDB Saver" as DynamoDBSaver
participant "Translate Service" as TranslateService
participant "AWS SNS" as SNS
participant "DynamoDB" as DynamoDB

User -> Frontend: Click vote button
Frontend -> AppSync: AddVote mutation
AppSync -> AddVoteResolver: Invoke AddVote
AddVoteResolver -> SNSPublisher: Publish vote event
SNSPublisher -> SNS: Publish message
AddVoteResolver -> DynamoDBSaver: Save vote data
DynamoDBSaver -> DynamoDB: PutItem (vote data)
AddVoteResolver -> TranslateService: Translate message
TranslateService -> AddVoteResolver: Translated message

AppSync -> Frontend: OnPlusOne subscription update

@enduml
```